Follow the steps below to install hadoop and related components (this is required/common for all nodes):
1. edit configure.sh and confgure the values base on target deployment environment
2. edit host_list_xxx.sh to configure the hostname and IP
3. run install_hadoop_common.sh with a user who has sudo privilege 


After the above is done, execute following additional steps based on the node type
-----------For named node----------
1. run install_hadoop_namenode.sh

-----------For datanode----------
1. run install_hadoop_datanode.sh
